# Cytroll default APT sources (Procursus rootless)
# {SUITE} is replaced at install time with the Procursus suite number
# (1800 for iOS 15, 1900 for iOS 16+) — matches BootstrapVersion.aptSuite.
# Verified format against https://apt.procurs.us/dists/{SUITE}/main/ (2026-07).

deb https://apt.procurs.us/ {SUITE} main

# ElleKit — tweak injection library/loader (provides mobilesubstrate).
# Procursus deliberately excludes hooking platforms/injection libraries
# from its own repo (removed ElleKit packaging upstream in 2024) to stay
# jailbreak-agnostic, so it must be seeded from its own official repo.
# Flat repo (no dists/ hierarchy) — verified against https://ellekit.space/Packages (2026-07).
deb https://ellekit.space/ ./

# Popular community repositories (optional — uncomment after bootstrap)
# deb https://repo.chariz.com/ ./
# deb https://havoc.app/ ./
